window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Faerie gangs are at war.</p> <p>The Seelie and Unseelie forces are tearing each other apart.</p> <p>Humanity is caught in the crossfire.</p> <p>I don't care which side wins. They're all assholes.</p> <p>But if they want to wage a war, they'll have to contend with me.</p> <p>And I'll be damned before I let either side get the upper hand.</p> <p><i>Bloody Bastards</i> is the fourth book in The Fury of a Vampire Witch. You've met Mercy before in The Legacy of a Vampire Witch and The Blood Witch Saga. She's fought against devils and demons, insidious witches, and old-world vampires. When she returns to Exeter, where she grew up as a girl, she'll find enemies even bigger and badder than anything she's ever faced before.</p>"; 
